textContent:
---birthmonth/8th month---

First letter in my birthmonth! Yayy!! Ang bilis talaga ng oanahon wth!! Parang kelan lang huhuhu. 

It's also our 8th month together tomorrow!! I'm really so excited for this month, just as excited I am excited with your birthday last month. I'm so excited to spend my special day with you bby!!! I'm sure it'll be the best one so far!!


---birthday ni mama---

I also want to thank you for spending time with my family! I really appreciate it kase alam kong di ka sanay sa lakad na super tagal HAHAHAHA. 

And also I want to let you know na I'm really really really thankful na you're my gf kase not only am I super happy and blessed with you, my entire family is too!! You are super kind and adorable and sweet and thoughtful, not only to me, but also to my family members! I'm really really thankful and happy for that bby. I love you so much!!

Kita mo naman jusko, sa sobrang saya ni mama sayo, apo na hinihinging regalo HAHAHAHAHAHAHA
